OL,3,CHolyrood committee backs 'necessary'
OL,4,Cabortion buffer zones Bill at stage one
OL,6,FA proposed law to ban protests outside
OL,7,Fabortion clinics is "necessary" to
OL,8,Fensure women are free of intimidation,
OL,9,Fa Holyrood committee has said.
OL,11,FThe Health, Social Care and Sport
OL,12,FCommittee has unanimously agreed to
OL,13,Fthe general principles of the Abortion
OL,14,FServices (Safe Access Zones) Bill
OL,15,Fproposed by Scottish Green MSP Gillian
OL,16,FMackay.
