OL,3,CHolyrood committee backs 'necessary'
OL,4,Cabortion buffer zones Bill at stage one
OL,6,FA report published by the committee on
OL,7,FMonday considered the conflicting
OL,8,Fhuman rights arguments relevant to the
OL,9,FBill, but ultimately concluded they
OL,10,Fare "proportionate" to the
OL,11,Flegislation's aims of ensuring women
OL,12,Fare able to safely access healthcare.
OL,14,FCommittee MSPs acknowledged the
OL,15,Fconcerns raised by opponents of the
OL,16,FBill who said the proposals threaten
OL,17,Ftheir freedom to express their views
OL,18,Fin public spaces.
