OL,6,FMSPs also questioned why the Bill
OL,7,Fproposes a 200-metre safe access zone,
OL,8,Finstead of the 150m recommended by
OL,9,Fexperts, with the exception of Queen
OL,10,FElizabeth University Hospital in
OL,11,FGlasgow which might need the radius
OL,12,Fextended due to its layout.
OL,14,FDuring the evidence gathering process,
OL,15,Fthe committee heard concerns that
OL,16,Fpolice may find it difficult to
OL,17,Fdetermine whether the law has been
OL,18,Fbreached by those undertaking silent
OL,19,Fprayers.
