OL,3,CHolyrood committee backs 'necessary'
OL,4,Cabortion buffer zones Bill at stage one
OL,6,FMSPs also heard from doctors working
OL,7,Fat facilities offering abortion
OL,8,Fservices, who raised concerns that
OL,9,Fprotests outside premises could result
OL,10,Fin patients delaying or not accessing
OL,11,Ftreatment, while women who had used
OL,12,Fthe services reported anxiety.
OL,14,FThe report states committee MSPs had a
OL,15,F"difference of views" over the issue
OL,16,Fof silent prayers, with some
OL,17,Fsuggesting it should be an explicit
OL,18,Fexemption to avoid the
OL,19,F"criminalisation of private thoughts".
