OL,3,CHolyrood committee backs 'necessary'
OL,4,Cabortion buffer zones Bill at stage one
OL,6,FMeanwhile, others said silent prayers
OL,7,F"can still be intimidating" to those
OL,8,Fseeking abortion services. The
OL,9,Fcommittee therefore recommended the
OL,10,Fissue is discussed further at stage
OL,11,Ftwo.
OL,13,FThe report went on to state that the
OL,14,FBill's implementation should be
OL,15,Fsubject to ongoing post-legislative
OL,16,Fscrutiny to ensure the restrictions
OL,17,Fremain proportionate.
OL,19,FIt will now proceed through the
OL,20,FScottish Parliament to be voted on at
OL,21,Fstage one.
