OL,3,CHolyrood committee backs 'necessary'
OL,4,Cabortion buffer zones Bill at stage one
OL,6,FClare Haughey, committee convener,
OL,7,Fsaid: "Our committee is united in
OL,8,Fbacking the Abortion Services (Safe
OL,9,FAccess Zones) Bill.
OL,11,F"We recognise the strong views it has
OL,12,Fgenerated and that not all are in
OL,13,Ffavour of its introduction.
OL,15,F"But ultimately we believe the
OL,16,Fcreation of safe access zones around
OL,17,Fabortion services is necessary to
OL,18,Fenforce the principle that everyone
OL,19,Fshould be able to access healthcare
OL,20,Ffree from intimidation or harassment.
OL,26,@oD@GOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
