OL,6,F"We understand there are competing
OL,7,Fhuman rights at play, but we have
OL,8,Fconcluded this Bill strikes an
OL,9,Fappropriate balance.
OL,11,F"We held extensive discussions on the
OL,12,Fissue of silent prayer and while some
OL,13,Fmembers felt this should be exempt
OL,14,Ffrom the provisions in this Bill,
OL,15,Fother members felt an exemption would
OL,16,Ffundamentally undermine its purpose
OL,17,Fand that silent prayer can be
OL,18,Fintimidating to those accessing
OL,19,Fservices.
